message.body: What's the plan?
Hello! So I got home and just finished eating. You're done at nine right?
Yeah
Are you gonna come?
How late are you planning to stay out?
I don't know yet. Maybe Like 2 hours or something. And im meeting her at 9:45
That might be a bit too late for me now. I talked to Xuan earlier and we're planning to meet at 8:30 tomorrow. Are you going in at 3 tomorrow and Wednesday? I want to hang.
Thats okay. Tomorrow before working, im meeting a friend and then have to help taryn with something. I can wednesday before 3
Okay! Well what are you doing now until you meet Taryn?
I went shopping with Staci my manager at fro gro
Hahahah awwww!
Whats that?
So, I'm pedantic.
A word I came across tonight that I realized can be used to describe me!
I just looked it up.
Oh my god yes you are
I know!!!
Hahah imagine me sitting here thinking "that sounds familiar..."
Jk jk hahah
I just went straight to "that's me"!
Ahaha yeah it's perfect. I didn't know a word like that existed
Well it does, and it begins with a "p". You know else begins with a "p"? Phuong!
Why yes it does. Pedantic Phuong.
Hahah!
I popped a melatonin 10 minutes ago. I'm hoping it'll kick in so I can get up by 8!
I hope you got up in time! I fell asleep as soon as I hit the pillow
Yup, I'm up, brushed, dressed, and ready to go! I did too, with the help of melatonin and about an hour or two's wait for it to kick in.
Haha well good. I'm glad that stuff works for you a bit
Me too! I'm hoping that since it's a vitamin, it'll be a healthier alternative.
I'm sure it is
I think we've lived in the city too long.
